y":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"說好的<br />\n海外華人去撚左邊"},{"pid":"ed66130ce5673d5fbecef52c11df1be06020772e","tid":326322,"uid":65934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁李波係咪英國籍？</blockquote><br />\n香港人有第二國藉係要去ID renounce 中國藉 （ 對香港人好唔fair) <br />\n只要有一日你未renounce nationality <br />\n龍門一日任佢放<br />\nEven if 你無中國藉 其實大陸一樣咁野蠻 上次果個瑞典人就係咁困咗佢好耐"},{"pid":"0bb932ffa27c56b9035fbe113d16325fdae54ecc","tid":326322,"uid":27363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"去外國被人拉係唔係可以即時洗走支那藉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac403a35f21a5027c763e851c6d501f64c6a1520","tid":326322,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"大陸d野任佢講<br />\n不具有中國籍<br />\n同<br />\n不承認雙重國籍<br />\n根本兩樣野"},{"pid":"8f77ff01b33c535d076f38afdf77d3ee4a1b10cb","tid":326322,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfab4f623eda91a42eef042644966d5bd4f11ed","tid":326322,"uid":67302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"公義真理於中國人就好似雞咁<br />\n鐘意叫就叫，鐘意唔叫就唔叫<br />\n心情好未講公義道德囉<br />\n平時就耍無賴"},{"pid":"a0a691d980789a44c44c5aa23c5ff934eff66304","tid":326322,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfac068eb7634e2dde02161d34a43a460bf9435b","tid":326322,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"靠你就死撚得喇小支支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581f20500b99e6fb29bd115d9eb28cc52fac51fa